    {"@type":"Question","name":"What is the process for ordering a custom robotic system?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Contact us with your product dimensions and weight, cleaning machine model, required throughput, and facility layout. We provide a design proposal covering robot selection, end-effector design, magazine design, and control integration, followed by a quotation and lead time."}}
